            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">六祖壇經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">六祖大師法寶壇經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>門人 法海 編集</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>後學 德清 勘校</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         自序品第一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    時，大師至寶林，韶州韋刺史與官僚，入山請師；出於城中大梵寺講堂，為眾\n開緣說法。師升座次，刺史官僚三十餘人、儒宗學士二十餘人、僧尼道俗一千餘人，\n同時作禮，願聞法要。大師告眾曰：『善知識！菩提自性，本水清淨，但用此心，直\n了成佛。善知識！且聽惠能行由得法事意。』惠能嚴父，本貫范陽，左降流于嶺南，\n作新州百姓；此身不幸，父又早亡，老母孤遺，移來南海；艱辛貧乏，於市賣柴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　時，有一客買柴，使令送至客店；客收去，惠能得錢，卻出門外，見一客誦\n經。惠能一聞經語，心即開悟，遂問：「客誦何經？」客曰：「金剛經。」復問：\n「從何所來，持此經典？」客云：「我從嶄州黃梅縣東禪寺來。其寺是五祖忍大\n師在彼主化，門人一千有餘；我到彼中禮拜，聽受此經。大師常勸僧俗，但持金\n剛經，即自見性，直了成佛。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  「惠能聞說，宿昔有緣，乃蒙一客，取銀十兩與惠能，令充老母衣糧，教便\n往黃梅參禮五祖。」「惠能安置母畢，即便辭違，不經三十餘日，便至黃梅，禮\n拜五祖。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  祖問曰：「汝何才人。欲求何物？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  惠能對曰：「弟子是嶺南新州百姓，遠水禮師，惟求作佛，不求餘物。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    祖言：「汝是嶺南人，又是獦獠，若為堪作佛？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    惠能曰：「人雖有南北，佛性本無南北；獦獠身與和尚不同，佛性有何差利？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    五祖更欲與語，且見徒眾總在左右，乃令隨眾作務。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    惠能曰：「惠能啟和尚，弟子自心，常生智慧，不離自性，即是福田。未審\n和尚教作何務？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    祖云：「這獦獠根性大利，汝更勿言，看槽廠去。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    惠能退至後院，有一行者，差惠能破柴踏碓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    八月餘日，祖一日忽見惠能曰：「吾思汝之見可用，恐有惡人害汝，遂不與\n汝言，汝知之否？」惠能曰：「弟子亦知師意，不敢行至當前，令人不覺。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    祖一日喚諸門人總來：「吾向汝說，世人生死事大，汝等終日只求福田，不\n求出離生死苦海，自性若迷，福何可救？汝等各去自看智慧，取自本心般若之性，\n各作一偈，來呈吾看。若悟大意，付汝衣法，為第六代祖。火急速去，不得遲滯；\n思量即不中用，見性之人，言下須見，若如此者，輪刀上陣，亦得見之。 」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    眾得處分，退而遞相謂曰：「我等眾人，不須澄心用意作偈，將呈和尚，有\n何所益？神秀上座，現為教授師，必是他得。我輩設作偈頌，枉用心力。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    諸人聞語，總皆息心，咸言：「我等已後依止秀師，何煩作偈？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    神秀思惟：「諸人不呈偈者，為我與他為教授師，我須作偈，將呈和尚，若\n不呈偈，和尚如何知我心中凡解深淺？我呈偈意，求法即善，覓祖即惡，卻同凡\n心，奪其聖位奚別？若不呈偈，終不待法。大難大難！」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    五祖堂前，有步廊三間，擬請供奉盧珍，畫楞伽變相，及五祖血  圖，流傳\n供養。神秀作偈成已，數度欲呈，行至堂前，心中恍惚，遍身汗流，擬呈不得；\n前後經四日，一十三度呈偈不得。秀乃思惟：「不如向廊下書著，從他和尚看見。\n忽若道好，即出禮拜，云是秀作；若道不堪，枉向小中數年，受人禮拜，更修何\n道？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    是夜三更，不使人知，自執燈，書偈於南廊壁間，呈心所見。偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    「身是菩提樹，心如明鏡臺，\n      時時勤拂拭，勿使惹塵埃。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　秀書偈了，便卻歸房，人總不知。秀復思惟：「五祖明日見偈歡喜，即我與\n法有緣；若言不堪，自是我迷，宿業障重，不合得法。」聖意難測，房中思想，\n坐臥不安，直至五更。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  祖已知神秀入門未得，不見自性。天明，祖喚盧供奉來，向南廊壁問，繪畫\n圖相，忽見其偈，報言：「供奉卻不用畫，勞爾遠水。經云：「凡所有相，皆是虛\n妄。」但留此偈，與人誦持，依此偈修。免墮惡道，依此偈修，有大利益。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    令門人炷香禮敬，盡誦此偈，即得見性，門人誦偈，皆歎善哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    祖，三更喚秀入堂，問曰：「偈是汝作否？」秀言：「實是秀作，不敢妄求祖\n位，望和尚慈悲，看弟子有少會慧否？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    祖曰：「汝作此偈，未見本性，只到門外，未入門內。如此見解，覓無上菩\n提，了不可得；無上菩提，須得言下識自本心，凡自本性，不生不滅。於一切時\n中，念念自凡，萬法無滯，一其勿一其，萬境白如如。如如之心，印是其實，若\n如是見，即是無上菩提之自性也。汝且去，一兩日思惟，更作一偈，將來吾看；\n汝偈若入得門，付汝衣法。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    神秀作禮而出。又經數日，作偈不成，心中恍惚，神思</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>不安，猶如夢中，行坐不樂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  一復兩日，有一童子於碓坊過，唱誦其偈；惠能一聞，便知此偈未見本性，\n雖未蒙教授，早識大意。遂問童子曰：「誦者何偈？」童子曰：「爾這獦獦不知，\n大師言，世人生死事大，欲得傳付衣法，令門人作偈來看。若悟大意，即付衣法\n為第六祖。神秀上座，於南廊壁上，書無相偈，大師令人皆誦，依此偈修，免墮\n惡道；依此偈修，有大利益。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">  　惠能曰：「上人！我此踏碓，八箇餘月，未曾行到堂前，望上人引至偈前禮\n拜。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  童子引至偈前禮拜，惠能曰：「惠能不識字，請上人為讀。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">  　時，有江州別駕，姓張名日用，便高聲讀。惠能聞己，遂言：「亦有一偈，\n望別駕為書。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  別駕言：「汝亦作偈，其事希有！」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　  惠能向別駕言：「欲學無上菩提，不得輕於初學。下下人有上上智，上上人\n有沒意智。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　別駕言：「汝但誦偈，吾為汝書。汝若得法，先須度吾，勿忘此言。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  惠能偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    「菩提本無樹，明鏡亦非臺，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>      本來無一物，何處惹塵埃。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　  書此偈已，徒眾總驚，無不嗟訝，各相謂言：「奇哉！不得以貌取人，何得\n多時，使他肉身菩薩。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  祖見眾人驚怪，恐人損害，遂將鞋擦了偈，曰：「亦未見性。」眾以為然。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　次日，祖潛至碓坊，見能腰石舂米，語曰：「求道之人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>，當如是乎？」乃問曰：「米熟也未？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  惠能曰：「米熟久矣，猶欠篩在。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   祖以杖擊碓三下而去。惠能即會祖意，三鼓入室；祖以袈裟遮圍，不令人見，<br>\n\n為說金剛經。至「應無所住而生其心」，惠能言下大悟，一切萬法，不離自性。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   遂啟祖言：「何期自性，本自清淨；何期自性，本不生滅；何期自性，本自<br>\n\n具足；何期自性，本無動搖；何期自性，能生萬法。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   祖知悟本性，謂惠能曰：「不識本心，學法無益；若識自本心，見自本性，<br>\n\n即名丈夫、天人師、佛。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  三更受法，人盡不知，便傳頓教及衣缽。云：「汝為第六代祖，善自護念，廣<br>\n\n度有情，流布將來，無令斷絕。聽吾偈曰：<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   『有情水下種，因地果還生，<br>\n\n     無情亦無種，無性亦無生。』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　祖復曰：「昔達磨大師，初來此土，人未之信，故傳此衣，以為信體，代代相\n承。法則以心傳心，皆令自悟自解。自古，佛佛惟傳本體，師師密付本心；衣為\n爭端，止汝勿傳。若傳此衣，命如懸絲，汝須速去，恐人害汝。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  惠能啟曰：「向甚處去？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　祖云：「逢懷則止，遇會則藏。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　三更，領得衣缽，五祖送至九江驛，祖令上船，惠能隨即把艣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　祖云：「合是吾渡汝。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   惠能云：「迷時師度，悟了自度；度名雖一，用處不同。惠能生在邊才，語<br>\n\n音不正，蒙師付法！今已得悟，只合向性自度。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   祖云：「如是，如是。以後佛法，由汝大行矣。汝今好去，努力向南，不宜<br>\n\n速說，佛法難起。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　惠能辭違祖已，發足南行，兩月中間，至大庾嶺逐後數百人來，欲奪衣缽。\n一僧俗姓陳，名惠明，先是四品將軍，性行麤燥，極意參尋，為眾人先，趨及惠\n能。惠能擲下衣缽，隱草莽中。惠明至，提不動，乃喚云：「行者！行者！我為\n法來，不為衣來。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">  　惠能遂出，坐盤石上。惠明作禮云：「望行者為我說法。」惠能曰：「汝既為\n法而來，可屏息諸緣，勿生一念，吾為汝說。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　明良久，惠能曰：「不思善，不思惡，正與麼時，那個是明上座本來面目？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   惠明言下大悟。復問云：「上來密語密意外，還更有密意否？」惠能云：「與<br>\n\n汝說者，即非密也。汝若返照，密在汝邊。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   明曰：「惠明雖在黃梅，實未省自己面目，今蒙指示，如人飲水，冷暖自知。<br>\n\n今行者，即惠明師也。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p> 　 惠能曰：「汝若如是，吾與汝同師黃梅，善自護持。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　明又問：「惠明今後向甚處去？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p> 　 惠能曰：「逢袁則止，遇蒙則居。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    明禮辭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    惠能後至曹溪，又被惡人尋逐，乃於四會，避難獵人隊中，凡經一十五載，\n時與獵人隨宜說法。獵人常令守網，每見生命，盡放之。每至飯時，以菜寄煮肉\n鍋。或問，則對曰：「但喫肉邊菜。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    一日思惟：「時當弘法，不可終避。」遂出至廣州法性寺；值印宗法師，講\n涅槃經。因二僧論風幡義，一曰風動，一曰幡動，議論不已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    惠能進曰：「不是風動，不是幡動，仁者心動。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    一眾駭然，印宗延至上席，徵詰奧義，見惠能言簡理當，不由文字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    宗云：「行者定非常人，久聞黃梅衣法南來，莫是行者否？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    惠能曰：「不敢！」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    宗於是作禮，告請傳來衣缽，出示大眾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    宗復問曰：「黃梅付囑？如何指授？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    惠能曰：「指授即無，惟論見性，不論禪定解脫。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    宗曰：「何不論禪定解脫？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    謂曰：「為是二法，不是佛法，佛法是不二之法。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    宗又問：「如何是佛法不二之法？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    惠能曰：「法師講涅槃經，明佛性是佛法不二之法。如高貴德王菩薩白佛言：\n「犯四重禁，作五逆罪，及一闡提等，當斷善根佛性否？」佛言：『善根有二：\n一者常，二者無常；佛性非常非無常，是故不斷，名為不二。』一者善，二者不\n善；佛性非善非不善，是名不二。蘊之與界，凡夫見二，智者了達其性無二；無\n二之性，即是佛性。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    印宗聞說，歡喜合掌，言：「某甲講經，猶如瓦礫；仁者論義，猶如其金。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    於是為惠能剃髮，願事為師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    「惠能遂於菩提樹下，開東山法門。惠能於東山得法，辛苦受盡，命似懸絲，\n今日得與史君官僚僧尼道俗同此一會，莫非累劫之緣？亦是過去生中，供養諸\n佛，同種善根，方始得聞如上頓教得法之因。教是先聖所傳，不是惠能自智。願\n聞先聖教者，各令淨心。聞了，各自除疑，如先代聖人無別。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    一眾聞法，歡喜作禮而退。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">            般若品第二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    次日，韋使君請益。師陞坐，告大眾曰：『總淨心念摩訶般若波羅蜜多。』\n復云：『善知識，菩提般若之智，世人本自有之，只緣心迷，不能自悟，須假大\n善知識，示導見性。當知愚人智人，佛性本無差別，只緣迷悟不同，所以有愚有\n智。吾今為說『摩訶般若波羅蜜』法，使汝等各得智慧。志心諦聽，吾為汝說─\n─</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     善知識，世人終日口念般若，不識自性般若；猶如說食不飽，口但說空，\n萬劫不得見性，終無有益。善知識，『摩訶般若波羅蜜』是梵語，此言大智慧到\n彼岸。此須心行，不在口念。口念心不行，如幻如化，如露如電。口念心行，則\n心口相應，本性是佛，離性無別佛。何名『摩訶』？『摩訶』是大。心量廣大，\n猶如虛空，無有邊畔，亦無方圓大小，亦非青黃赤白，亦無上下長短，亦無瞋無\n喜，無是無非，無善無惡，無有頭尾。諸佛剎土，盡同虛空。世人妙性本空，無\n有一法可得；自性真空，亦復如是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，莫聞吾說空，便即著空。第一莫著空，若空心靜坐，即著無記空。\n善知識，世界虛空，能含萬物色像。日月星宿，山河大地、泉源溪澗、草木叢林、\n惡人善人、惡法善法、天堂地獄、一切大海、須瀰諸山、總在空中；世人性空，\n亦復如是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，自性能含萬法是大，萬法在諸人性中。若見一切人惡之與善，盡皆\n不取不捨，亦不染著，心如虛空名之為大，故約『摩訶』。善知識，迷人口說，\n智者心行，又有迷人，空心靜坐，百無所思，自稱為大；此一輩人，不可與語，\n為邪見故。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    善知識，心量廣大，遍周法界；用了即了了分明，應用便知一切。一切即一，\n一即一切；來去自由，心體無滯，即是般若。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，一切般若智，皆從自性而生，不從外入，莫錯用意，名為  行性自\n用。一真一切真。心量大事，不行小道。口莫終日說空，心中不   修此行；恰\n似凡人，自稱國王，終不可得，非吾弟子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，何名『般若』？『般若者，唐言智慧也。』一切處所，一切時中，\n念念不愚，常行智慧，即是般若行。一念愚，即般若絕；一念智，即般若生。世\n人愚迷，不見般若；口說般若，心中常愚。常自言我修般若，念念說空，不識真\n空。般若無形相，智慧心即是。若作如是解，即名般若智。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">   何名『波羅蜜』？此是西國語，唐言到彼岸，解義離生滅。著境生滅起，如\n水有波浪，即名於此岸，離境無生滅，如水常流通，即名為彼岸，故號『波羅蜜』。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  善知識，迷人口念，當念之時，有妄有非。念念若行，是名真性。悟法者，是<br>\n\n般若法；修此行者，是般若行；不修即凡。一念修行，自身等佛。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    善知識，凡夫即佛，煩惱即菩提。前念迷，即凡夫；後念悟，即佛。前念著\n境，即煩惱；後念離境，即菩提。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，『摩訶般若波羅蜜』，最尊最上最第一，無住無往亦無來，三世諸佛\n從中出。當用大智慧，打破五蘊煩惱塵勞。如此修行，定佛道，變三毒為戒\n定慧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，我此法門，從一般若，生八萬四千智慧。何以故？為世人有八萬四\n千塵勞。若無塵勞，智慧常現，不離自性。悟此法者，即是無念、無憶、無著。\n不起誑妄，用自真如性，以智慧觀照；於一切法，不取不捨。即是見性成佛道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，若欲入甚深法界，及般若三昧者，須修般若行。持誦《金剛般若經》\n即得見性，當知此經功德無量無邊，經中分明讚嘆，莫能具說。此法門是最上乘，\n為大智人說，為上根人說；小智小根人聞，心生不信。何以故？譬如天龍下雨於\n閻浮提，城邑聚落，悉皆漂流，如漂草葉；若雨大海，不增不減。若大乘人，若\n最上乘人，聞說《金剛經》，心開悟解故，知本性自有般若之智，自用智慧，常\n觀照故，不假文字。譬如雨水，不從天有，元是龍能興致，令一切眾生，一切草\n木，有情無情，悉皆蒙潤，百川眾流，卻入大海，合為一體。眾生本性般若之智，\n亦復如是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，小根之人，聞此頓教，猶如草木，根性小者，若被大雨，悉皆自倒，\n不能增長。小根之人，亦復如是。元有般若之智，與大智人更無差別。因何聞法\n不自開悟？緣邪見障重，煩惱根生。猶如大雲覆蓋於日，不得風吹，日光不現。\n般若之智亦無大小，為一切眾生自心迷悟不同。迷心外見，修行覓佛，未悟自性，\n即是小根；若開悟頓教，不執外修，但於自心常起正見，煩惱塵勞，常不能染，\n即是見性。善知識，內外不住，去來自由，能除執心，通達無礙，能修此行，與\n《般若經》本無差別。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，一切修多羅及諸文字、大小二乘、十二部經，皆因人置。因智慧性，\n方能建立。若無世人，一切萬法本自不有，故知萬法本自人興；一切經書，因人\n說有。緣其人中，有愚有智；愚為小人，智為大人；   愚者問於智人，智者為\n愚人說法；愚人忽然悟解心開，即與智人無別。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，不悟，即佛是眾生；一念悟時，眾生是佛。故知萬法盡在自心，何\n不從心中頓見真如本性？《菩薩戒經》云：『我本元自性清淨，若識自心見性，\n皆成佛道』《淨名經》云：『即時豁然，還得本心』。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，我於忍和尚處，一聞言下便開悟，頓見真如本性。是以將此教法流\n行，令學道者頓悟菩提，各自觀心，自見本性。若自不悟，需覓大善知識，解最\n上乘法者，直示正路，是善知識有大因緣。所謂化導令得見性，一切善法，因善\n知識能發起故。三世諸佛、十二部經，在人性中本自具有，不能自悟，須求善知\n識指示方見；若自悟者，不假外求。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    若一向執謂須他善知識望得解脫者，無有是處。何以故？自心內有知識自\n悟，若起邪迷，妄念顛倒，外善知識雖有教授，救不可得；若起真正般若觀照，\n一剎那間，妄念俱滅。若識自性，一悟即至佛地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    善知識，智慧觀照，內外明徹，識自本心。若識本心，即本解脫；若得解脫，\n即是般若三昧；般若三昧即是無念。何名無念？若見一切法，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>心不染著，是為無念。用即[偏]一切處，亦不著一切處；但淨本心，使六識出六\n門，於六塵中，無染無雜，來去自由，通用無滯，即是般若三昧。自在解脫，名\n無念行。若百物不思，當令念絕，即是法縛，即名邊見。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    善知識，悟無念法者，萬法盡通；悟無念法者，見諸佛境界；悟無念法者，\n至佛地位。善知識，後代得吾法者，將此頓教法們，於同見同行，發願受持，如\n事佛故，終身而不退者，定入聖位。然須傳授從上以來默傳分付，不得匿其正法；\n若不同見同行，在別法中，不得傳付。損彼前人，究竟無益。恐愚人不解，謗此\n法門，百劫千生，斷佛種性。善知識，吾有一無向頌，各須頌取，在家出家，但\n依此修；若不自修，惟記吾言，亦無有益。聽吾頌曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   說通即心通  如日處虛空  為傳見法性  出世破邪宗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   法即無頓漸  迷悟有遲疾  只此見性門  愚人不可悉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   說即雖萬般  合理還歸一  煩惱暗宅中  常須生慧日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   邪來煩惱至  正來煩惱除  邪正俱不用  清淨至無餘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   菩提本自性  起心即是妄  淨心在妄中  但正無三障</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   世人若修道  一切盡不妨  常自見己過  與道即相當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   色類自有道  各不相妨惱  離道別覓道  終生不見道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   波波度一生  到頭還自懊  欲得見真道  行正即是道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   若真修道人  不見世間過  若見他人非  自非卻是左</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   他非我不非  我非自有過  但自卻非心  打除煩惱破</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   憎愛不關心  長伸兩腳臥  欲擬化他人  自須有方便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   勿令彼有疑  即是自性現  佛法在世間  不離世間覺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   離世覓菩提  恰如求兔角  正見名出世  邪見名世間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   邪正盡打卻  菩提性宛然  此頌是頓教  亦名大法船</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   迷聞經累劫  悟則剎那間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     師復曰：『今於大梵寺說此頓教，普願法界眾生，言下見性成佛』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     時韋使君與官僚道俗，聞師所說，無不省悟。一時作禮，皆嘆哉！何期嶺南有佛出世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   ****系統難字 [偏] 原作 [彳扁]****</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">            決疑品第三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">     一日，韋刺史為師設大會齋。齋訖，剌丈請師升座，同官僚士庶，肅容再\n拜，問曰：『弟子聞和尚說法，實不可思議，今有少疑，願大慈悲，特為解說。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     師曰：『有疑即問，吾當為說。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     韋公曰：『和尚所說，可不是達摩大師宗旨乎？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     師曰：『是。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     公曰：『弟子聞達摩初化梁武帝，帝問云：「朕一生造寺度僧，布施設齋，\n有何功德？」達摩言：「實無功德。」弟子未達此理，願和尚為說。』師曰：『實\n無功德，勿疑先聖之言。武帝心邪，不知正法，造寺度僧，布施設齋，名為求福，\n不可將福便為功德。功德在法身中，不在修福。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師又曰：『凡性是功，平等是德；念念無滯，常見本性其實妙用，名為功德。\n內心謙下是功，外行於禮是德；自性建立萬法是功，心體離念是德；不離自性是\n功，應用無染是德；若覓功德法身，但依此作，是真功德。若修功德之人，心即\n不輕，常行普敬，心常輕人，吾我不斷即自無功；自性虛妄不實，即自無德；為\n吾我自大，常輕一切故。善知識！念念無間是功，心行平直是德；自修性是功，\n自修身是德。善知識！功德須自性內見，不是布施供養之所求也。是以福德與功\n德別，武帝不識其理，非我祖師有過。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    刺史又問曰：『弟子常見僧俗念阿彌陀佛，願生西方；請和尚說，得生彼否？\n願為破疑。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師言：『使君善聽，惠能與說。世尊在舍衛城中，說西方引化，經文分明去\n此不遠。若論相說里數有十萬八千，即身中十惡八邪，便是說遠。說遠，為其下\n根；說近，為其上智。人有兩種，法無兩般；迷悟有味，見有遲疾。迷人念佛，\n求生於彼；悟人自淨其心。所以佛言：「隨其心淨，即佛土淨。」使君東方人，\n但心淨即無罪；雖西方人，心不淨亦有愆。東方人造罪，念佛求生西方；西方人\n造罪，念佛求生何國？凡愚不了自性，不識身中淨土，願東願西，悟人在處一般。\n所以佛言：「隨所住處，恆安樂。」使君心地，但無不善，西方去此不遙；若懷\n不善之心，念佛往生難到。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">  『今勸善知識，先除十惡，即行十萬；後除八邪，乃過八千。念念見性，常行\n十直，到如彈指，便親彌陀。使君但行十善，何須更願往生？不斷十惡之心，仃\n佛印水迎請？若悟無生頓法，見西才只在剎那；不悟，念佛求生，路遙如何得達？\n惠能與諸人移西方如剎那間，目前便見，各願見否？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    皆頂禮云：『若此處見，何須更願往生？願和尚慈悲，便現西方，普令得見。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師言：『大眾！世人自色身是城，眼耳鼻舌是門；外有五門，內有意門；心\n是地，性是王；王居心地上。性在，王在；性去，王無。性在，身心存；性去，\n身心壞。佛向性中作，莫向身外求。自性迷，即是眾生；自性覺，即是佛。慈悲，\n即是觀音；喜捨，名為勢至。能淨，即釋迦；平直，即彌陀。人我是須彌，邪心\n是海水，煩惱是波浪，毒害是惡龍，虛妄是鬼神，塵勞是魚鼇，貪瞋是地獄，愚\n癡是畜生。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！常行十善，天堂便至，除人我，須彌倒；去邪心，海水竭；煩惱無，\n波浪滅；毒害忘，魚龍絕。自心地上，覺性如來，放大光明，外照六門清淨，能\n破六欲諸天。自性內照，三毒即除，地獄等罪，一時消滅，內外明徹，不異西方。\n不作此修，如何到彼？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    大眾聞說，了然凡性，悉皆禮拜，俱歎善哉！唱言：『普願法界眾生，聞者<br>\n\n一時悟解。』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師言：『善知識！若欲修行，在家亦得，不由在寺。在家能行，如東才人心<br>\n\n善；在寺不修，如西才人心惡，但心清淨，即是自性西方。』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    韋公又問：『在家如何修行，願為教授。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    師言：『吾與大眾，作無相頌，但依此修，常與吾同處無別。若不作此修，\n剃髮出家，於道何益？頌曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     「心平何勞持戒？行直何用修禪？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       恩則親養父母，義則上下相憐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       讓則尊卑和睦，忍則眾惡無喧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       若能鎖木出火，淤泥定生紅蓮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       苦口的是良藥，逆耳必是忠言。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       改過必生智慧，護短心內非賢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       日用常行饒益，成道非由施錢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       菩提只向心見，何勞向什求玄？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       聽說依此修行，天堂只在目前。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">     師復曰：『善知識！總須依偈修行，見取自性，直成佛道。法不相待，眾人\n且散，吾歸曹溪，眾若有疑，卻來相問。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     時，刺丈官僚，在會善男信女，各得開悟，信受奉行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">           定慧品第四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師示眾云：『善知識！我此法門，以定慧為本，大眾勿迷。言定慧別，定慧\n一體，不是二；定是慧體，慧是定用，即慧之時定在慧，即定之時慧在定。若識\n此義，即是定慧等學。諸學道人，莫言先定發慧，先慧發定各別。作此見者，法\n有二相，口說善語，心中不善，空有定慧，定慧不等；若心口俱善，內外一種，\n定慧即等。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『自悟修行，不在於諍；若諍先後，即同迷人。不斷勝負，卻增我法，不離四\n相。善知識！定慧猶如何等？猶如燈光。有燈即光，無燈即暗；燈是光之體，光\n是燈之用。名雖有 二，體本同一。此定慧法，亦復如走。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師示眾云：『善知識！一行三昧者，於一切處，行、住、坐、臥，常行一直\n心是也。如淨名經云：「直心是道場，直心是淨土。」莫心行諂曲，口但說直，\n口說一行三昧，不行直心；但行直心，於一切法，勿有執著。迷人著法相，執一\n行三昧。直言坐不動，妄不起，心即是一行三昧。作此解者。即同無情，卻是障\n道因緣。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師示眾云：『善知識！道須通流，何以卻滯？心不住法，道即通流；心若住\n法，名為自縛。若言坐不動，是只如舍利弗宴坐林中，卻被維摩誥訶。善知識！\n又有人教坐，看心觀靜，不動不起，從此置功，迷人不會，便執成顛。如此者眾，\n如是相教，故知大錯。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    師示眾云：『善知識！本來正教，無有頓漸，人性自有利鈍。迷人漸契，悟\n人頓修，自識本心，自見本性，即無差利，所以立頓漸之假名。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！我此法門，從上以來，先立無念為宗，無相為體，無住為本。無相\n者：於相而離相；無念者：於念而無念；無住者：人之本性，於世間善惡好醜，\n乃至冤之與親，言語觸刺欺爭之時，並將為空，不思酬害，念念之中，不思前境。\n若前念、今念、後念，念念相續不斷，名為繫縛。於諸法上，念念不住，即無縛\n也。此是以無住為本。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！外離一切相，名為無相；能離於相，即法體清淨；此是以無相為體。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！於諸境上心不染，曰無念；於自念上常離諸境，不於境上生心。若\n只百物不思，念盡除卻，一念絕即死，別處受生，是為大錯。學道者思之。若不\n識法意，自錯猶可，更勸他人，自迷不見，又謗佛經；所以立無念為宗。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！云何立無念為宗？只緣口說見性，迷人於境上有念，念上便起邪\n見，一切塵勞妄想，從此而生。自性本無一法可得；若有所得，妄說禍福，即是\n塵勞邪見。故此法門，立無念為宗。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！無者無何事？念者念何物？無者：無二相，無諸塵勞之心；念者，\n念其如本性。真如即是念之體，念即是真如之用。真如自性起念，非眼耳鼻舌能\n念，其如有性，所以起念；真如若無，眼耳色聲，當時即壞。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">  『善知識！真如自性起念，六根雖有見聞覺知，不染萬境，而真性常自在。故\n經云：『能善分別諸法相，於第一義而不動。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">           妙行品第五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     師示眾云：『此門坐禪，元不著心，亦不著淨，亦不是不動。若言著心，心\n元是妄，知心如幻，故無所著也。若言著淨，人性本淨，由妄念故，蓋覆真如，\n但無妄想，性自清淨。起心著淨，卻生淨妄，妄無處所，著者是妄。淨無形相，\n卻立淨相，言是工夫；作此見者，障自本性，卻被淨縛。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！若修不動者，但見一切人時，不見人之是非善惡過患，即是自性不\n動。善知識！迷人身雖不動，開口便說他人是非長短好惡，與道違背；若著心著\n淨，即障道也。』師示眾云：『善知識！何名坐禪？此法門中，無障無礙，外於\n一切善惡境界，心念不起，名為坐；內見自性不動，名為禪。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！何名禪定？外離相為禪；內不亂為定。外若著相，內心即亂；外若\n離相，心即不亂。本性自淨自定，只為見境思境即亂。若見諸境心不亂者，是真\n定也。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">  『善知識！外離相即禪，內不亂即定；外禪內定，是為禪定。菩薩戒經云：「我\n本性元自清淨。」善知識！於念念中，自見本性清淨，自修自行，自成佛道。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">           懺悔品第六</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     時，大師見廣韶洎四方士庶，駢集山中聽法，於是升座告眾曰：『來！諸善\n知識！此事須從自性中起。於一切時，念念自淨其心，自修自行，見自己法身，\n見自心佛，自度、自戒，始得不假到此。既從遠來，一會于此，皆共有緣，今可\n各各胡跪，先為傳自性五分法身香，次授無相懺悔。』眾胡跪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師曰：『一、戒香：即自心中無非、無惡、無嫉妒、無貪瞋、無劫害，名戒\n香。二、定香：即親諸善惡境相，自心不亂，名定香。三、慧香：自心無礙，常\n以智慧，觀照自性，不造諸惡，雖修眾善，心不執著，敬上念下，矜恤孤貧，名\n慧香。四、解脫香：即自心無所攀緣，不思善，不思惡，自在無礙，名解脫香。\n五、解脫知見香：自心既無所攀緣、善惡，不可沉空守寂，即須廣學多聞，識自\n本心，達諸佛理，和光接物，無我、無人，直至菩提，真性不易，名解脫知見香。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！此香各自內薰，莫向外覓。令與汝等授無相懺悔，滅三世罪，令得\n三業清淨。善知識！各隨語，一時道：「弟子等從前念、今念及後念，念念不被\n愚迷染；從前所有惡業愚迷等罪，悉皆懺悔，願一時消滅，永不復起。弟子等從\n前念、今念及後念，念念不被憍誑染；從前所有惡業憍誑等罪，悉皆懺悔，願一\n時消滅，永不復起。弟子等從前念、   今念及後念，念念不被嫉妒染；從前所\n有惡業嫉妒等罪，悉皆懺悔，願一時消滅，永不復起。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！已上是為無相懺悔。云何名懺？云何名悔？懺者：懺其前衍；從前\n所有惡業、愚迷、憍誑、嫉妒等罪，悉皆盡懺，永不復起，是名為懺。悔者：悔\n其後過；從今已後，所有惡業、愚迷、憍誑、嫉妒等罪，今已覺悟，悉皆永斷，\n更不復作，是名為悔，故稱懺悔。凡夫愚迷，只知懺其前衍，不知悔其後過。以\n不悔故，前衍不滅，後過又生。前衍   既不滅，後過復又生，何名懺悔？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">  『善知識！既懺悔已，與善知識發四弘誓願，各須用心正聽：自心眾生無邊誓\n願度，自心煩惱無邊誓願斷，自性法門無盡誓願學，自性無上佛道誓願成。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！大家豈不道，眾生無邊誓願度？怎麼道，且不是惠能度。善知識！\n心中眾生，所謂邪迷心、誑妄心、不善心、嫉妒心、惡毒心，如是等心，盡是眾\n生，各須自性自度，是名真度。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『何名自性自度？即自心中邪見、煩惱、愚癡、眾生，將正見度。既有正見，\n使般若智打破愚癡迷妄眾生，各各自度。邪來正度，迷來悟度，愚來智度，惡來\n善度；如是度者，名為真度。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『又，煩惱無邊誓願斷，將自性般若智，除卻虛妄思想心是也。又，法門無盡\n誓願學，須自見性，常行正法，是名真學。又，無上佛道誓願成，既常能下心行\n於真正，離迷、離覺，常生般若，除真、除妄，即見佛性，即言下佛道成。常念\n修行是願力法。善知識！今發四弘願了，更與善知識授無相三歸依戒。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！歸依覺，兩足尊；歸依正，離欲尊；歸依淨，眾中尊。從今日起，\n稱覺為師，更不歸依邪魔外道。以自性三寶，常自證明，勸善知識，歸依自性三\n寶。佛者覺也，法者正也，僧者淨也。自心歸依覺，邪迷不生，少欲知足，能離\n財色，名兩足尊。自心歸依正，念念無邪見，以無邪凡故，即無人我貢高貪愛執\n著，名離欲尊。自心歸依淨，一切塵    勞愛欲境界，自性皆不染著，名眾中尊。\n若修此行，是自歸依，凡夫不會，從口至夜，受三歸戒，若言歸依佛，佛在何處？\n若不見佛，憑何所歸？言卻成妄。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！各自觀察，莫錯用心。經文分明言、自歸依佛，不言歸依他佛。自\n佛不歸，無所依處。今既自悟，各須歸依自心三寶，內調心性，外敬他人，是自\n歸依也。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！既歸依自三寶竟，各各志心，吾與說一體三身自性佛，令汝等見三\n身，了然自悟自性，總隨我道：「於自色身，歸依清淨法身佛；於自色身，歸依\n千百億化身佛；於自色身，歸依圓滿報身佛。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！色身是舍宅，不可言歸向者。三身佛在自性中，世人總有為自心迷\n不見內性，外覓三身如來，不見自身中有三身佛。汝等聽說，令汝等於自身中見\n自性有三身佛。此三身佛，從自性生，不從外得。何名清淨法身佛？世人性本清\n淨，萬法從自性生；思量一切惡事，即生惡行；思量一切善事，即生善行。如是\n諸法，在自性中，如天常清，日月常明，為浮雲蓋覆，上明下暗，忽遇風吹雲散，\n上下俱明，萬象皆現；世人性常浮游，如彼天雲。善知識！智如日，慧如月；智\n慧常明，於外著境，被妄念浮雲蓋覆，自性不得明朗。若遇善知識，聞真正法，\n自除迷妄，內外明徹，於自性中，萬法皆現，見性之人，亦復如是。此名清淨法\n身佛。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！自心歸依自性，是皈依真佛。自皈依者，除卻自性中不善心、嫉妒\n心、諂曲心、吾我心、誑妄心、輕人心、慢他心、邪見心、貢高心及一切時中不\n善之行，常自見己過，不說他人好惡，是自皈依。常須下心，普行恭敬，即是見\n性通達，更無滯礙，是自皈依。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『何名千百億化身？若不思萬法性本如空，一念思量，名為變化。思量惡事，\n化為地獄；思量善事，化為天堂；毒害化為龍蛇；慈悲化為菩薩，智慧化為上界，\n愚癡化為下才。自性變化甚多，迷人不能省覺，念念起惡，常行惡道，回一念善，\n智慧即生，此名自性化身佛。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『何名圓滿報身？譬如一燈，能除千年暗，一智，能滅萬年愚。莫思向前，已\n過不可得；常思於後，念念圓明。自見本性，善惡雖殊，本性無二。無二之性，\n名為實性，於實性中，不染善惡，此名圓滿報身佛。自性起一念惡，滅萬劫善因；\n自性起一念善，得恆沙惡盡，直至無上菩提。念念自見，不失本念，名為報身。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『善知識！從法身思量，即是化身佛；念念自性自見，即是報身佛。自悟自修\n自性功德，是其歸依；皮肉是色身，色身是宅舍，不言歸依也。但悟自性三身，\n即識自性佛。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  『吾有一無相頌，若能誦持，言下令汝積劫迷罪，一時消滅。頌曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     「迷人修福不修道，  只言修福便是道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       布施供養福無邊，  心中三惡元來造；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       擬將修福欲滅罪，  後世得福罪還在。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       但向心中除罪緣，  各自性中真懺悔；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       忽悟大乘真懺悔，  除邪行正即無罪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       學道常於自性觀，  即與諸佛同一類。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       吾祖唯傳此頓法，  普願見性同一體；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       若欲當來覓法身，  離諸法相心中洗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       努力自見美悠悠，  後念忽絕一世休；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>       若悟大乘得見性。  虔恭合掌至心求。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>     師言：『善知識！總須誦取，依此修行，言下見性，雖去吾千里，如常在吾\n邊；於此言下不悟，即對面千里，何勤遠來？珍重，好去！』     一眾聞法，\n靡不開悟，歡喜奉行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">        機緣品第七</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師自黃梅得法，回至韶州曹侯村，人無知者。時，有儒士劉志略，禮遇甚厚。\n志略有姑為尼，名無盡藏，常誦大涅槃經。師暫聽，即知妙義，遂為解說；尼乃\n執卷問字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師曰：『字即不識，義即請問。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    尼曰：『字尚不識，曷能會義？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  師曰：『諸佛妙理，非關文字。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  尼驚異之，遍告里中耆德云：『此是有道之士，宜請供養。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  有魏武侯玄孫曹叔良及居民，競來瞻禮。時，寶林古寺，自隋末兵火已廢，\n遂於故基，重建梵宇，延師居之。俄成寶坊，師住九月餘日，又為惡黨尋逐。師\n乃遁于前山，被其縱火焚草木，師隱身挨入石中得免。石今有師趺坐膝痕及衣布\n之紋，因名避難石。師憶五祖懷會止藏之囑，遂行隱于二邑焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  僧法海，韶州曲江人也。初參祖師，問曰：『即心即佛，願垂指諭。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　  師曰：『前念不生即心，後念不滅即佛；成一切相即心離一切相即佛。吾若\n具說，窮劫不盡，聽吾偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  「即心名慧，即佛乃定；定慧等持，意中清淨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　  悟此法門，由汝習性；用本無生，雙脩是正。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  法海言下大悟，以偈讚曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　『即心元是佛，不悟而自屈，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　  我知定慧因，雙脩離諸物。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　僧法達，洪洲人，七歲出家，常誦法華經，來禮祖師；頭不至地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　祖訶曰：『禮不投地，何如不禮。汝心中必有一物，蘊習何事耶？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『念法華經，己及三千部。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　祖曰：『汝若念至萬部，得其經意，不以為勝，則與吾偕行。汝今負此事業，\n都不知過。聽吾偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　『禮本折慢幢，頭奚不至地；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  　有我罪即生，忘功福無比。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師又曰：『汝名什麼？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『名法達。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝名法達，何曾達法？』復說偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　『汝今名法達，勤誦未休歇，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　　空誦但循聲，明心號菩薩；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　　汝今有緣故，吾今為汝說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　　但信佛無言，蓮花從口發。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  達聞偈悔謝曰：『而今而後，當謙恭一切。弟子誦法華經，未解經義，心常<br>\n\n有疑，和尚智慧廣大，願略說經中義理。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  師曰：『法達，法即甚達，汝心不達；經本無疑，汝心自疑。汝念此經，以<br>\n\n何為宗？』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　達曰：『學人根性暗鈍，從來但依文誦念，豈知宗趣？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『吾不識文字，汝試取經誦之一遍，吾當為汝解說。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　法達即高聲念經，至譬喻品，師曰：『止！此經元來以因緣出世為宗，縱說\n多種譬喻，亦無越於此。何者因緣？經云：「諸佛世尊，唯以一大事因緣故，出\n現於世。」一大事者，佛之知見也。世人外迷著相，內迷著空；若能於相離相，\n於空離空，即是內外不迷。若悟此法，一念心開，是為開佛知見。佛，猶覺也；\n分為四門：開覺知見、示覺知見、悟覺知見、入覺知見。若聞開示便能悟入，即\n覺知見，本來真性，而得出現。汝慎勿錯解經意，見他道開示悟入，自是佛之知\n見，我輩無分。若作此解，乃是謗經毀佛也。彼既是佛，已具知見，何用更開？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　汝今當信佛知見者，只汝自心，更無別佛。蓋為一切眾生，自蔽光明，貪愛\n塵境，外緣內擾，甘受驅馳，便勞他世尊從三昧起，種種苦口，勸令寢息，莫向\n外求，與佛無二；故云開佛知見。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　吾亦勸一切人，於自心中，常開佛之知見；世人心邪，愚迷造罪，口善心惡，\n貪瞋嫉妒諂佞我慢，侵入害物，自開眾生知見。若能正心常生，智慧觀照，自心\n止惡行善，是自開佛之知見。汝須念念開佛知見，勿開眾生知見。開佛知見，即\n是出世；開眾生知見，即是世間，汝若但勞勞執念，以為功課者，何異犛牛愛尾？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　達曰：『若然者，但得解義，不勞誦經耶？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　師曰：『經有何過，豈障汝念？只為迷悟在人，損益由己。口誦心行，即是\n轉經；口誦心不行，即是被經轉。聽吾偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　「心迷法華轉，心悟轉法華，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　　誦經久不明，與義作讎家；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　　無念念即正，有念念成邪，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　　有無俱不計，長御白牛車。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　達聞偈，不覺悲泣，言下大悟，而告師曰：『法達從昔已來，實未曾轉法華，\n乃被法華轉。』再啟曰：『經云：「諸大聲聞乃至菩薩，皆盡思共度量，不能測佛\n智。」今令凡夫但悟自心，便名佛之知見，自非上根，未免疑謗。又經說三車，\n羊鹿之車與白牛之車，如何區利？願和尚再垂開示。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『經意分明，汝自迷背。諸三乘人，不能測佛智者，患在度量也，鐃\n伊盡思共推，轉加懸遠。佛本為凡夫說，不為佛說，此理若不肯者，從他退席，\n殊不知坐卻白牛車，更於門外覓三車。況經文明向汝道，唯一佛乘，無有餘乘。\n若二若二乃至無數，方便種種因緣譬喻言詞，是法皆為一佛乘故。汝何不省？三\n車是假，為昔時故；一乘是實，為今時故。只教汝去假歸真，歸真之後，真亦無\n名。應知所有珍財，盡屬於汝，由汝受用，更不作父想，亦不作子想，亦無用想；\n是名持法華經。從劫至劫，手不釋卷，從晝至夜，無不念時也。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　達蒙啟發，踴躍歡喜，以偈讚曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　『經誦三千部，曹溪一句亡，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　  未明出世旨，寧歇累生狂；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　  羊鹿牛權設，初中後善揚，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　  誰知火宅內，元是法中王。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝今後才可名念經僧也。』達從此領玄旨，亦不輟誦經。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　僧智通，壽州安豐人，初看楞伽經約千餘遍，而不會三身四智，禮師求解其義。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『三身者：清淨法身：汝之性也；圓滿報身，汝之智也；千百億化身，\n汝之行也。若離本性，別說三身，即名有身無智；若悟三身無有自性，即名四智\n菩提。聽吾偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　「自性具三身，發明成四智，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　  不離凡聞緣，超然登佛地；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　  吾今為汝說，謗信永無迷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　  莫學駛求者，終日說菩提。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　通再啟曰：『四智之義，可得聞乎？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　師曰：『既會三身，便明四智，何更問耶？若離三身，別談四智，此名有智\n無身。即此有智，還成無智。』復偈曰﹕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　『大圓鏡智性清淨，千等性智心無病，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　　妙觀察智見非功，成所作智同圓鏡；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　　五八六七果因轉，但用名言無實性，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　　若於轉處不留情，繁興永處那伽定。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　『如上轉識為智也。教中云：「轉前五識為成所作智，轉第六識為妙觀察智，\n轉第七識為平等性智，轉第八識為大圓鏡智。」雖六七因中轉，五八果上轉；但\n轉其名，而不轉其體也。』通頓悟性智，遂呈偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　『三身元我體，四智本心明，\n  　　身智融無礙，應物任隨形；\n  　　起脩皆妄動，守住匪真精，\n  　　妙旨因師曉，終亡染污名。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　僧志常，信州貴谿人，髫年出家，志求凡性；一日參禮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師問曰：『汝從何來？欲求何事？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　曰：『學人近往洪州白峰山禮大通和尚，蒙示見性成佛之義，未決狐疑，遠\n來投禮，伏望和尚指示。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『彼有何言句，汝試舉看。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　曰：『智常到彼，凡經三月，未蒙示誨。為法切故，一夕，獨入丈室，請問\n如何是某甲本心本性？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　大通乃曰：「汝見虛空否？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　對日：「見」。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　彼曰：「汝見虛空有相貌否？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　對曰：「虛空無形，有何相貌？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　彼曰：「汝之本性，猶如虛空，了無一物可見，是名正見；無一物可知，是\n名真知。無有青黃長短，但見本源清淨，覺體圓明，即名見性成佛，亦名如來知\n見。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　學人雖聞此說，猶未決了，乞和尚開示。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『彼師所說，猶存見知，故今汝未了。吾今示汝一偈：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　「不見一法存無見，大似浮雲遮日面，\n　　　不知一法守空知，還如太虛生閃電；\n　　　此之知見瞥然興，錯認何曾解方便，\n　　　汝當一念自知非，自己靈光常顯現。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　常聞偈己，心意豁然，乃述偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　『無端起知見，著相求菩提，\n　　　情存一念悟，寧越昔時迷；\n　　　自性覺源體，隨服枉遷流，\n　　　不入祖師室，茫然趣兩頭。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　智常一日問師曰：『佛說三乘法，又言最上乘，弟子未解，願為教授。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝觀自未心，莫著外法相，法無四乘，人心自有等差。凡聞轉誦，\n是小乘；悟法解義，是中乘；依法修行，是大乘。萬法盡通，萬法俱備，一切不\n染，離諸法相，一無所得，名最上乘。乘是行義，不在口爭，汝須自修，莫問吾\n也，一切時中，自性自如。』常禮謝執侍，終師之世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　僧志道，廣州南海人也，請益曰：『學人自出家，覽涅槃經，十載有餘，未\n明大意，願和尚垂誨。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝何處未明？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『諸行無常，是生滅法，生滅滅已，寂滅為樂；於此疑惑。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝作麼生疑？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『一切眾生，當有二身；謂色身、法身也。色身無常，有生有滅；法身\n有常，無知無覺。經云：「生滅滅已，寂滅為樂」者，不審何身寂滅？何身受樂？\n若色身者，色身滅時，四大分散，全然是苦，苦不可言樂。若法身寂滅，印同草\n木瓦石，誰當受樂？又，法性是生滅之體，五蘊是生滅之用；一體五用，生滅是\n常；生則從體起用，滅則攝用歸體。若聽更生，即有情之類，不斷不滅；若不聽\n更生，則永歸寂滅，同於無情之物。如是則一切諸法被涅槃之所禁伏，尚不得生，\n何樂之有？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師曰：『汝是釋子，何習外道斷常邪見，而議最上乘法？據汝所說，即色身\n外別有法身，離生滅求於寂滅；又推涅槃常樂，言有身受用，斯乃執吝生死，耽\n著世樂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　汝今當知，佛為一切迷人，認五蘊和合為自體相；分別一切法為外塵相。好\n生惡死，念念遷流，不知夢幻虛假，枉受輪迴，以常樂涅槃，翻為苦相，終日馳\n求；佛愍此故，乃示涅槃真樂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　『剎那無有生相，剎那無有滅相，更無生滅可滅，是則寂滅現前，當現前時，\n亦無現前之量，乃謂常樂。此樂無有受者，亦無不受者，豈有一體五用之名？何\n況更言涅槃禁伏諸法，令永不生，斯乃謗佛毀法。聽吾偈曰：「</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    無上大涅槃，圓明常寂照，凡愚謂之死，外道執為斷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　諸求二乘人，目以為無作，盡屬情所計，六十二見本。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　妄立虛假名，何為真實義？惟有過量人，通達無取捨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　以知五蘊法，及以蘊中我，外現眾色像，一一音聲相。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　平等如夢幻，不起凡聖見，不作涅槃解，二邊三際斷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　常應諸根用，而不起用想，分別一切法，不起分別想。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　劫火燒海底，風鼓山相擊，真常寂滅樂，涅槃相如是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　吾今強言說，令汝捨邪見，汝勿隨言解，許汝知少分。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　志道聞偈大悟，踴躍作禮而退。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　行思禪師，生吉州安城劉氏，聞曹溪法席盛化，徑來參禮，遂問曰：『當何\n所務，即不落階級？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝曾作什麼來？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『聖諦亦不為。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『落何階級？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『聖諦尚不為，何階級之有？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師深器之，令師首眾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　一日，師謂曰：『汝當分化一方，無令斷絕。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　思既得法，遂回吉州青原山，弘法紹化，諡號弘濟禪師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　懷讓禪師，金州杜氏子也。初謁嵩山安國師，安發之曹溪參扣。讓至，禮拜，\n師曰：『甚處來？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『嵩山。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『什麼物，怎麼來？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『說似一物即不中。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『還可修證否？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『修證即不無，污染即不得。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『只此不污染，諸佛之所護念；汝既如是，吾亦如是。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  讓豁然契會，遂執侍左右一十五載，日臻玄奧；後往南嶽，大闡禪宗，敕諡<br>\n\n大慧禪師。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  永嘉玄覺禪師，溫州戴氏子。少習經論，精天臺止觀法門，因看維摩經，發<br>\n\n明心地。偶師弟子玄策相訪，與其劇談，出言暗合諸祖。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　策云：『仁者得法師誰？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『我聽方等經論，各有師承；後於維摩經，悟佛心宗，未有證明者。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　策云：『威音王已前即得，威音王已後，無師自悟，盡是天然外道。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　云：『願仁者為我證據。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　策云：『我言輕，曹溪有六祖大師，四方雲集，並是受法者，若去，則與偕\n行。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　覺遂同策來參，遶師三匝，振鍚而立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『夫沙門者，具二千成儀，八萬細行；大德自何方而來，生大我慢？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　覺曰：『生死事大，無常迅速。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『何不體取無生，了無速乎？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『體即無生，了本無速。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『如是，如是！』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　玄覺方具威儀禮拜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    須臾告辭，師曰：『返大速乎？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『本自非動，豈有速耶？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『誰知非動？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    曰：『仁者自生分別。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝甚得無生之意。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『無生豈有意耶？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『無意誰當分別？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    曰：『分別亦非意。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『善哉！少留一宿。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　時謂一宿覺，後著證道歌，盛行于世；謚曰無相大師，時稱為其覺焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    禪者智隍，初參五祖，自謂已得正受，庵居長坐，積二十年。師弟子玄策游\n方至河朔，聞隍之名，造庵問云：『汝在此作什麼？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　隍曰：『入定。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　策云：『汝云入定，為有心人耶？無心人耶？若無心人者，一切無情草木瓦\n石，應合得定；若有心人者，一切有情含識之流，亦應得定。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　隍曰：『我正入定時，不見有有無之心。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　策云：『不見有有無之心，即是常定，何有出入？若有出入，即非大定。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　隍無對，良久，問曰：『師嗣誰耶？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　策云：『我師曹溪六祖。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　隍云：『六祖以何為禪定？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　策云：『我師所說，妙湛圓寂，體用如如；五陰本空，六塵非有；不出不入，\n不定不亂；禪性無住，離住禪寂；禪性無生，離生禪想；心如虛空，亦無虛空之\n量。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　隍聞是說，徑來謁師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師問云：『仁者何來？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　隍具述前緣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師云：『誠如所言。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　師憫其遠來，遂垂開決。隍於是大悟，二十年所得心都無影響。其夜、河北\n士庶，聞空中有聲云：『隍禪師今日得道。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　隍後禮辭，復歸河北，開化四眾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　有一童子，名神會，襄陽高氏子，年十二，白玉泉來參禮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師曰：『知識遠來艱辛，還將得本來否？若有本則合識主，試說看。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    會曰:『以無住為本，見即是主。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    師曰：『這沙彌爭合取次語。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　會乃問曰：『和尚坐禪，還見不見？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師以柱打三下云：『吾打汝是痛不痛？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　對曰：『亦痛，亦不痛。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『吾亦見，亦不見。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　神會問：『如何是亦見，亦不見？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師云：『吾之所見，常見自心過愆，不見他人是非好惡；是以亦見亦不見。\n汝言亦痛亦不痛，如何？汝若不痛，同其木石；若痛，則同凡夫，即起恚恨。汝\n向前見不見，是二邊；痛不痛，是生滅。汝自性且不見，敢爾弄人？』神會禮拜\n悔謝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師又曰：『汝若心迷不見，問善知識覓路；汝若心悟，即自見性，依法修行。\n汝自迷不見自心，卻來問吾見與不見。吾見自知，豈待汝迷？汝若自見，亦不待\n吾迷，何不自知自見，乃問吾見與不見？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　神會再禮百餘拜，求謝過愆，服勤給侍，不離左右。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　一日，師告眾曰：『吾有一物，無頭無尾，無名無字，無背無面，諸人還識否？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　神會出曰：『是諸佛之本源，神會之佛性。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　師曰：『向汝道無名無字，汝便喚作本源佛性。汝向去有把茆蓋頭，也只成\n箇知解宗徒。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　祖師滅後，會入京洛，大弘曹溪頓教，著顯宗記，盛行于世；是謂荷澤禪師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　一僧問師曰：『黃梅意旨，甚麼人得？』師云：『會佛法人得。』僧云：『和尚還得否？』師云：『我不會佛法。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　師一日欲濯所授之衣，而無美泉；因至寺後五里許，見山林鬱茂，瑞氣盤旋；\n師振鍚卓地，泉應手而山，積以為池，乃跪膝浣衣石上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　有蜀僧才辯謁師，師曰：『上人攻何事業？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　曰：『善塑。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師正色曰：『汝試塑看。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　辯罔措。過數日，塑就真相，可高七寸，曲盡其妙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師笑曰：『汝善塑性，不解佛性。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　即為摩頂授記，永與人天為福田，仍以衣酬之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　辯取衣分為三：『一披塑像，一自留，一用繌裹痊地中。誓曰：『後得此衣，\n乃吾出世，住持於此，重建殿宇。』宋嘉祐八年，有僧惟先，修殿掘地，得衣如\n新。像在高泉寺，祈禱輒應。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　有僧舉臥輪禪師偈云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　『臥輪有伎倆，能斷百思想，\n  　　對境心不起，菩提日日長。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師聞之曰：『此偈未明心地，若依而行之，是加繫縛。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　因示一偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　『惠能沒伎倆，不斷百思想，\n  　　對境心數起，菩提作麼長。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">        頓漸品第八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  時，祖師居曹溪寶林；神秀大師在荊南玉泉寺。于時兩宗盛化，人皆稱南能<br>\n\n北秀；故有南北二宗頓漸之分，而學者莫知宗趣。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  師謂眾曰：『法本一宗，人有南北，法即一種，見有遲疾；何名頓漸？法無<br>\n\n頓漸，人有利鈍，故名頓漸。』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　然秀之徒眾，往往譏南宗祖師不識一字，有何所長？秀曰：『他得無師之智，\n深悟上乘，吾不如也。且吾師五祖，親傅衣法，豈徒然哉！吾恨不能遠去親近，\n虛受國恩。汝等諸人，毋滯於此，可往曹溪參決。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　一日，命門人志誠曰：『汝聰明多智，可為吾到曹溪聽法；若有所聞，盡心\n記取，還為吾說。』志誠稟命至曹溪，隨眾參請，不言來處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　時，祖師告眾曰：『今有盜法之人，潛在此會。』志誠即出禮拜，具陳其事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝從玉泉水，應是細作。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　對曰：『不是！』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『何得不是？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　對曰：『未說即走，說了不是。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『汝師若為示眾？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　對曰：『常指誨大眾，住心觀淨，長坐不臥。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　師曰：『住心觀淨，是病非禪；長坐拘身，於理何益？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>聽吾偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　「生來坐不臥，死去臥不坐，\n　　　元是臭骨頭，何為立功過。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　志誠再拜曰：『弟子在秀大師處學道九年，不得契悟；今聞和尚一說，便契\n本心。弟子生死事大，和尚大慈，更為教示！』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  師曰：『吾聞汝師教示學人戒定慧法，未審汝師說戒定慧行相如何？與吾說看。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    誠曰：『秀大師說，諸惡莫作名為戒，諸善奉行名為慧，自淨其意名為定，\n彼說如此，未審和尚以何法誨人？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　  師曰：『吾若言有法與人，即為誑汝。但且隨才解縛，假名三昧。如汝師所\n說戒定慧，實不可思議，吾所見戒定慧又別。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　志誠曰：『戒定慧只合一種，如何更別？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師曰：『汝師戒定慧，接大乘人；吾戒定慧，接最上乘人。悟解不同，見有遲\n疾；汝聽吾說，與彼同否？吾所說法，不離自性；離體說法，名為相說；自性常\n迷，須知一切萬法，皆從自性起用，是真戒定慧法，聽吾偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　「心地無非自性戒，心地無癡自性慧，\n　  心地無亂自性定，不增不減自金剛，\n  　身去身來本三昧。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　誠聞偈悔謝，乃呈一偈：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　『五蘊幻身，幻何究竟？迴趣真如，法還不淨。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　 師然之。復語誠曰：『汝師戒定慧，勸小根智人；吾戒定慧，勸大智根人；若\n悟自性，亦不立菩提涅槃，亦不立解脫知見。無一法可得，才能建立萬法；若解\n此意，亦名菩提涅槃，亦名解脫知見。見性之人，立亦得，不立亦得，去來自由，\n無滯無礙；應用隨作，應語隨答；普見化身，不離自性，即得自在神通，游戲二\n昧；是名見性。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  志誠再啟師曰：『如何是不立義？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>師曰：『自性無非、無癡、無亂；念念般若觀照，常離法相，自由自在，縱橫盡\n得，有何可立？自性自悟，頓悟頓脩，亦無漸次，所以不立一切法。諸法寂滅，\n有何次第？』志誠禮拜，願為執侍，朝夕不懈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  一僧志徹，江西人，本姓張，名行昌，少任仗；自南北分化，二宗主雖亡彼我，\n而徒侶競起愛憎。時，北宗門人，自立秀師為第六祖，而忌祖師傳衣為天下聞，\n乃囑行昌來剌師。師心通，預知其事，即置金十兩於座間。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  時，夜暮，行昌入祖室，將欲加害，師舒頸就之。行昌揮刃者三，悉無所損。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  師曰：『正劍不邪，邪劍不正；只負汝金，不負汝命。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　行昌驚仆，久而方蘇，求哀悔過，即願出家。師遂與金，言：『汝且去，恐徒\n眾翻害於汝，汝可他日易形而來，吾當攝受。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　行昌稟旨宵遁，後投僧出家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　一日，憶師之言，遠木禮覲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師曰：『吾久念汝，汝來水何晚？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　曰：『昨蒙和尚捨罪，今雖出家苦行，終難報德，其惟傳法度生乎？弟子常覽\n涅槃經，未曉常無常義，乞和尚慈悲，略為解說。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師曰：『無常者，即佛性也；有常者，即一切善惡諸法分別心也。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　曰：『和尚所說，大違經文。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師曰：『吾傳佛心印，安敢違於佛經？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p> 曰：『經說佛性是常，和尚卻言無常；善惡諸法，乃至菩提心，皆是無常，和<br>\n\n尚卻言是常；此即相違，令學人轉加疑惑。』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p> 師曰：『涅槃經，吾昔聽尼無盡藏讀誦一遍，便為講說，無一宇一義不合經文，<br>\n\n乃至為汝，終無二說。』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　曰：『學人識量淺昧，願和尚委曲開示。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師曰：『汝知否？佛性若常，更說什麼善惡諸法，乃至窮劫，無有一人發菩提\n心者；故吾說無常，正是佛說真常之道也。又一切諸法若無常者，即物物皆有自\n性，客受生死，而真常性有不遍之處；故吾說常者，正是佛說真無常義。佛比為\n凡夫外道，執於邪常；諸二乘人，於常計無常，共成八倒故，於涅槃了義教中，\n破彼偏見，而顯說真常、真樂、真我、真淨。汝今依言背義，以斷滅無常，及確\n定死常，而錯解佛之圓妙最後微言，縱覽千遍，有何所益？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　行昌忽然大悟，說偈云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　『因守無常心，佛說有常性，\n　  不知方便者，猶春池拾礫；\n　  我今不施功，佛性而現前，\n　  非師相授與，我亦無所得。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　師曰：『汝今徹也，宜名志徹。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　徹禮謝而退。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師見諸宗難問，咸起惡心，多集座下，愍而謂曰：『學道之人，一切善念惡念，\n應當盡除；無名可名，名於自性；無二之性，是名實性，於實性上，建立一切教\n門，言下便須自見。』諸人聞說，總皆作禮，請事為師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">        護法品第九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>    神龍元年上元日，則天中宗詔云：『朕請安秀二師，宮中供養，萬幾之暇，\n每究一乘。二師推讓云：「南方有能禪師，密授忍大師衣法，傳佛心印，可請彼\n問。」今遣內侍薛簡，馳詔迎請。願師慈念，速赴上京。』　師上表辭疾，願終\n林麓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　  薛簡曰：『京城禪德皆云：「欲得會道，必須坐禪習定；若不因禪定而得解脫\n者，未之有也。」未審師所說法如何？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  師曰：『道由心悟，豈在坐也？經云：「若言如來若坐若臥，是行邪道。」何\n故？無所從來，亦無所去；無生、無滅，是如來清淨禪；諸法空寂，是如來清淨\n坐，究竟無證，豈況坐耶？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　簡曰：『弟子回京，主上必問，願師慈悲指示心要，傳奏兩宮，及京城學道者；\n譬如一燈，然百千燈，冥者皆明，明明無盡。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   師云：『道無明暗，明暗是代謝之義；明明無盡，亦是有盡，相待立名。故<br>\n\n淨名經云：「法無有比，無相待故。」』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p> 簡曰：『明喻智慧，暗喻煩惱，脩道之人，倘不以智慧照破煩惱，無始生死，<br>\n\n憑何出離？』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p> 師曰：『煩惱即是菩提，無二無別。若以智慧照破煩惱者，此是二乘見解，羊<br>\n\n鹿等機，上智大根，悉不如是。』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　簡曰：『如何是大乘見解？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　 師曰：『明與無明，凡夫見二；智者了達，共性無二，無二之性，即是實性。\n實性者：處凡愚而不減，在賢聖而不增，住煩惱而不亂，居禪定而不寂。不斷、\n不常、不來、不去，不在中間及其內外；不生、不滅，性相如如，常住不遷，名\n之曰道。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　 簡曰：『師曰不生不滅，何異外道？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　 師曰：『外道所說不生不滅者，將滅止生，以生顯滅，滅猶不滅，生說不生。\n我說不生不滅者，本自無生，今亦不滅，所以不同外道。汝若欲知心要，但一切\n善惡，都莫思量，自然得入清淨心體，湛然常寂，妙用恒沙。』簡蒙指教，豁然\n大悟，禮辭歸闕，表奏師語。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　其年九月三日，有詔獎諭師曰：『師辭老疾，為朕修道，國之福田，師若淨名，\n托疾毗耶，闡揚大乘，傳諸佛心，談不二法，薛簡傳師指授如來知見，朕積善餘\n慶，宿種善根，值師出世，頓悟上乘。感荷師恩，頂戴無已，並奉磨納袈裟，及\n水晶缽，敕韶州刺史脩寺宇，賜師舊居，為國恩寺焉。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">     付囑品第十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>   師，一日喚門人法海、志誠、法達、神會、智常、智通、志徹、志道、法珍、\n法如等曰：『汝等不同餘人，吾滅度後，各為一方師。吾今教汝說法，不失本宗，\n先須舉三科法門，動用三十六對，出沒即離兩邊，說一切法莫離自性。忽有人問\n汝法，出語盡雙，皆取對法，來去相因，究竟三法盡除，更無去處。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　『三科法門者，陰界入也。陰是五陰：色受想行識是也。入是十二入，外六塵：\n色、聲、香、味、觸、法；內六門：眼、耳、鼻、舌、身、意是也。界是十八界：\n六塵、六門、六識是也。自性能含萬法，名含藏識；若起思量，即是轉識。生六\n識，出六門，見六塵，如是一十八界，皆從自性起用。自性若邪，起十八邪；自\n性若正，走十八正。若惡用即眾生用，善用即佛用。用由何等，由自性有。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　『對法外境，無情五對：天與地對，日與月對，明與暗對，陰與陽對，水與火\n對，此是五對也。法相語言十二對：語與法對，有與無對，有色與無色對，有相\n與無相對，有漏與無漏對，色與空對，動與靜對，清與濁對，凡與聖對，僧與俗\n對，老與少對，大與小對，此是十二對也。自性起用十九對：長與短對，邪與正\n對，癡與慧對，愚與智對，亂與定對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>，慈與毒對，戒與非對，直與曲對，實與虛對，險與平對，煩惱與菩提對，常與\n無常對，悲與害對，喜與嗔對，捨與慳對，進與退對，生與滅對，法身與色身對，\n化身與報身對，此是十九對也。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  師言：『此三十六對法若解用，即通貫一切經法，出入即離兩邊，自性動用，\n共人言語，外於相離相，內於空離空，若全著相。即長邪見，若全執空，即長無\n明。執空之人，有謗經直言不用文字，即云不用文字，人亦不合語言，只此語言，\n便是文字之相。又云直道不立文字，即此不立兩字，亦是文字，見人所說，便即\n謗他言著文字。汝等須知，自迷猶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>可，又謗佛經，不要謗經，罪障無數。若著相於外，而作法求真，或廣立道場，\n說有無之過患，如是之人，累劫不可見性，但聽依法修行，又莫百物不思，而於\n道性窒礙。若聽說不修，令人反生邪念，但依法修行，無住相法施。汝等若悟，\n依此說，依此用，依此行，依此作，即不失本宗。若有人問汝義，問有，將無對；\n問無，將有對；問凡，以聖對；問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>聖，以凡對。二道相因，生中道義，汝一問一對，餘問一依此作，即不失理也。\n設有人問：「何名為暗？」答云：「明是因，暗是緣，明沒則暗，以明顯晦，以暗\n顯明，來去相因，成中道義。餘問，悉皆如此。」汝等於後傳法，依此轉相教授，\n勿失宗旨。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  師於大極元年壬子延和七月命門人往新州國恩寺建塔，仍令促工。次年夏末\n落成。七月一日，集徒眾曰：『吾至八月，欲離世間，汝等有疑，早須相問，為\n汝破疑，令汝迷盡。吾若去後，無人教汝。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  法海等聞，悉皆涕泣，惟有神會，神情不動，亦無涕泣。師云：『神會小師，\n卻得善不善等，毀譽不動，哀樂不生，餘者不得。數年山中，竟脩何道？汝今悲\n泣，為憂阿誰？若憂吾不知去處，吾自知去及；吾若不知去處，終不預報於汝。\n汝等悲泣，蓋為不知吾去處；若知吾去處，即不合悲泣。法性本無生滅去來，汝\n等盡坐，吾與汝說一偈，名曰「真假動靜偈。」汝等誦取此偈，與吾意同，依此\n脩行，不失宗旨。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　眾僧作禮，請師作偈，偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　『一切無有真，不以見於真，若見於真者，是見盡非真。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">   若能自有真，離假即心真，自心不離假，無真何處真？<br>\n\n   有情即解動，無情即不動，若脩不動行，同無情不動。<br>\n\n   若覓真不動，動上有不動，不動走不動，無情無佛種。<br>\n\n   能善分別相，第一義不動，但作如此見，即是真如用。<br>\n\n   報諸學道人，努力須用意，莫於大乘門，卻執生死智。<br>\n\n  若言下相應，即共論佛義，若實不相應，合掌令歡喜。<br>\n\n  此宗本無諍，諍即失道意，執逆諍法門，自性入生死。』<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　時，徒眾聞說偈已，普皆作禮，並體師意，各各攝心，依法脩行，更不敢諍，\n乃知大師不久住世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　法海上座再拜問曰：『和尚入滅之後，衣法當付何人？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師曰：『吾於大梵寺說法以至于今，抄錄流行，目曰：「法寶壇經」，汝等守護，\n遞相傳授，度諸群生，但依此說，是名正法。今為汝等說法，不付其衣，蓋為汝\n等信根淳熟，決定無疑堪任大事。然據先祖達磨大師付授偈意，衣不合傳。侷曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　「吾本來茲土，傳法救迷情，\n　  一花開五葉，結果自然成。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師復曰：『汝等若欲成就種智，須達一相三昧，一行三昧。若於一切處而不住\n相，於彼相中不生憎愛，亦無取捨，不念利益成壞等事，安閑恬靜，虛融澹泊，\n此名一相三昧。若於一切處行住坐臥，純一直心不動道場，其成淨土，此名一行\n三昧。若人具二三昧，如地有種，今藏長養，成熟其實，一相一行，亦復如是。\n我今說法，猶如時雨，普潤大地，汝等佛性，譬諸種子，遇茲霑洽，悉皆發生。\n承吾旨者，決獲菩提；依吾行者，定證妙果。聽吾偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　「心地含諸種，普雨悉皆萌，\n  　頓悟花情已，菩提果自成。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師說偈已，曰：『其法無二，其心亦然，其道清淨，亦無諸相。汝等慎勿觀靜，\n及空其心；此心本淨，無可取捨，各自努力，隨緣好去。』　爾時，徒眾作禮而\n退。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　大師，七月八日，忽謂門人曰：『吾欲歸新州，汝等速理舟楫。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　大眾哀留甚堅，師曰：『諸佛出現，猶示涅槃；有來必去，理亦常然。吾此形\n骸，歸必有所。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　眾曰：『師從此去，早晚可回。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  師曰：『葉落歸根，來時無口。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  又問曰：『正法眼藏，傳付何人？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師曰：『有道者得，無心者通。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　問曰：『未知從上佛祖應現已來，傳授幾代，願垂開示。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師云：『古佛應世，已無數量，不可計也。今以七佛為始。過去莊嚴劫毘婆尸\n佛、尸棄佛、毗舍浮佛；今賢劫拘留孫佛、拘那含牟尼佛、迦葉佛、釋迦文佛是\n為七佛。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　『釋迦文佛首傳摩訶迦葉尊者 第二、阿難尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　第三、商那和修尊者  　　第四、優波(毛匊)多尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第五、提多迦尊者        第六、彌遮迦尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第七、婆須蜜多尊者      第八、佛馱難提尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第九、伏馱蜜多尊者      第十、(月劦)尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第十一、富那夜奢尊者    第十二、馬嗚大士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第十三、迦毗摩羅尊者    第十四、龍樹大士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第十五、迦那提婆尊者    第十六、羅(目侯)羅多尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第十七、僧伽難提尊者    第十八、伽耶舍多尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第十九、鳩摩羅多尊者    第二十、闍耶多尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第二十一、婆脩盤頭尊者  第二十二、摩拏羅尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第二十三、鶴勒那尊者    第二十四、師子尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第二十五、婆舍斯多尊者  第二十六、不如蜜多尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第二十七、般若多羅尊者  第二十八、菩提達磨尊者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第二十九、慧可大師      第三十、僧璨大師</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  第三十一、道信大師      第三十二、弘忍大師</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>惠能是為三十三祖。從上諸祖，各有稟承，汝等向後遞代流傳，毋令乖誤。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  又問：『此後無有難否？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師曰：『吾滅後五六年，當有一人，欲取吾首。聽吾讖曰：「頭上養親，口裡須\n餈，遇滿之難，楊柳為官。」』大師，先天二年癸丑歲八月初三日－是年十二月，\n改元開元－於國恩寺齋罷，謂諸徒眾曰：『汝等各依位坐，吾與汝別。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　法海自言：『和尚留何教法，令後代迷人，得見佛性？』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師言：『汝等諦聽，後代迷人，若識眾生，即是佛性；若不識眾生，萬劫覓佛\n難逢。吾今教汝識自心眾生，見自心佛性。欲求見佛，但識眾生；只為眾生迷佛，\n非是佛迷眾生。自性若悟，眾生是佛；自性若迷，佛是眾生。自性平等，眾生是\n佛；自性邪險，佛是眾生。汝等心若險曲，即佛在眾生中，一念平直，即是眾生\n成佛。我心自有佛，自佛是真佛，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>自若無佛心，何處求真佛？汝等自心是佛，更莫狐疑，外無一物而能建立，皆是\n本心生萬種法。故經云：「心生，種種法生；心滅，種種法滅。」吾今留一偈，\n與汝等別，名「自性真佛偈」。後代之人，識此偈意，自見本心，自成佛道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　「真如自性是真佛，邪見二毒是魔王，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　邪迷之時魔在舍，正見之時佛在堂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　性中邪見三毒生，即是魔王來住舍，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　正見自除三毒心，魔變成佛真無假。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　法身報身及化身，三身本來是一身，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　若向性中能自見，即是成佛菩提因。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　本從化身生淨性，淨性常在化身中，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　性使化身行正道，當來圓滿真無窮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　婬性本是淨性因，除妊即是淨性身，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　性中各自離五欲，見性剎那即是真。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　　今生若遇頓教門，忽悟自性見世尊，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  若欲修行覓作佛，不知何處擬求真。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　若能心中自見真，有真即是成佛因，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  不見自性外覓佛，起心總是大癡人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  　頓教法門今已留，救度世人須自修，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  報汝當來學道者，不作此見大悠悠。」』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師說偈已，告曰：『汝等好住，吾滅度後，莫作世情悲泣雨淚，受人弔問。身\n著孝服，非吾弟子，亦非正法。但識自本心，見自本性，無動無靜，無生無滅，\n無去無來，無是無非，無住無往。恐汝等心迷，不會吾意，今再囑汝，令汝見性。\n吾滅度後，依此修行，如吾在日；若違吾教，縱吾在世，亦無有益。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>  復說偈曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　『兀兀不修善，騰騰不造惡，\n　  寂寂斷見聞，蕩蕩心無著。』</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　師說偈已，端坐至三更，忽謂門人曰：『吾行矣！』奄然遷化，于時異香滿室，\n白虹屬地，林木變自，禽獸哀嗚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　十一月，廣韶新三郡官僚，洎門人緇白，爭迎真身，莫決所之。乃焚香禱曰：\n『香煙指處，師所歸焉。』時，香煙直貫曹溪。十一月十三日，遷神龕併所傳衣\n缽而回。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　  次年七月二十五日出龕，弟子才辯，以香泥上之。門人憶念取首之記，遂先\n以鐵葉漆布，固護師頸入塔。忽於塔內，白光出現，直上衝天，三日始散。韶州\n奏聞，奉敕立碑紀師道行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>　師，春秋七十有六，年二十四傳衣，三十九祝髮，說法利生三十七載。得旨嗣\n法者，四十三人，悟道超凡者，莫知其數。達磨所傳信衣，中宗賜磨納寶缽，及\n才辯塑師真相，並道具等，主塔侍者尸之，永鎮寶林道場。流傳壇經，以顯宗旨，\n興隆三寶，普利群生者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">End of the Project Gutenberg EBook of Liu Zu Tan Jing, by Hui-Neng Shi</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>*** END OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK LIU ZU TAN JING ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>***** This file should be named 23844-0.txt or 23844-0.zip *****\nThis and all associated files of various formats will be found in:\n        http://www.gutenberg.org/2/3/8/4/23844/</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>Produced by Jia-Fu Xu</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-f09fcd twpub-e1a0e9084e6a1b6e-6b4cd0\"><p>Updated editions will replace the previous one—the old editions\nwill be renamed.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e1a0e9084e6a1b6e/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
